title: Match history
body:
For a Couple weeks now I Haven't been able to check my online match history, it comes up completely blank.
http://puu.sh/pUDda/e0b5414f7d.jpg
Currently on the boards there's a few Rito posts saying that it's fixed for said person who noted their match history was derping. But no posts explaining to anyone with the issue how to get it fixed for themselves.
It makes me sad because I'm not able to go back and look at what I have built in previous games or gloat to my friends LOOK AT MY DAMAGE THAT GAME and fun Ego Boosts like that. :(

replies.body:
Hey there,

Are you still experiencing this issue?

Could you please visit the URL below and paste the output of that page into a reply here (Please remove your IP from the reply) so that I can forward this info onto the live services team to have a look at.

http://matchhistory.oce.leagueoflegends.com/cdn-cgi/trace
Not sure if it is Relevant at the moment, it has been almost 2 weeks since  I even opened league, and the match history now works, sorry for the failure to reply.
